Phòng Chờ thế?

185
00:09:09,842 --> 00:09:11,719
- Chúc chị mau khoẻ nha.
- Cảm ơn em.

186
00:09:11,802 --> 00:09:13,512
- Bác sĩ.
- Cảm ơn.

187
00:09:13,679 --> 00:09:15,598
Cảm ơn.

188
00:09:15,681 --> 00:09:16,807
